[I] Perl module Exception-Class

[T] This module allows you to declare hierarchies of exception classes for
[T] use in your code. It also provides a simple exception class that it
[T] uses as the default base class for all other exceptions.

[U] https://search.cpan.org/~drolsky/Exception-Class-1.23/

